OL,3,CScotland has suffered nearly 7,000
OL,4,Cdays of failure under SNP, Findlay says
OL,6,FScotland has endured nearly 7,000 days
OL,7,Fof failure and division under the SNP,
OL,8,FRussell Findlay has said as he marked
OL,9,F19 years since the party took office.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Conservative leader
OL,12,Faccused John Swinney's party of having
OL,13,Fa "reverse Midas touch" that has seen
OL,14,Fpublic services decline while taxes
OL,15,Frise.
OL,17,FMr Findlay said the country could not
OL,18,Fafford another five years of SNP rule.
OL,26,@uD@COUuD@WO]
