OL,3,CScotland has suffered nearly 7,000
OL,4,Cdays of failure under SNP, Findlay says
OL,6,FHe urged pro-UK voters to back his
OL,7,Fparty on the list vote which he said
OL,8,Fcould stop the SNP forming a majority
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FHe said: "This unhappy anniversary is
OL,12,Fa grim reminder that Scotland has
OL,13,Fendured almost 7,000 days of failure
OL,14,Fand division under the SNP.
OL,16,F"The country can't afford five more
OL,17,Fyears of John Swinney.
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@AOU
