OL,3,CScotland has suffered nearly 7,000
OL,4,Cdays of failure under SNP, Findlay says
OL,6,F"Our NHS is in permanent crisis,
OL,7,Feducation standards have plummeted as
OL,8,Fclassroom violence soars, our roads
OL,9,Fare scarred by potholes, and crime is
OL,10,Frising while prisoners are freed early.
OL,12,F"And that's before you get to record
OL,13,Fdrug deaths, the ferries scandal,
OL,14,Fsoaring taxes and the never-ending
OL,15,Fobsession with tearing Scotland out of
OL,16,Fthe UK.
OL,18,F"The SNP have a reverse Midas touch `
OL,19,Fthe more money they take off hard-
OL,20,Fworking Scots, the worse our public
OL,21,Fservices get.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
