OL,3,CScotland has suffered nearly 7,000
OL,4,Cdays of failure under SNP, Findlay says
OL,6,F"There's no chance of the mess being
OL,7,Ffixed if Swinney wins the majority he
OL,8,Freckons is in the bag, because his
OL,9,Fsole focus will be holding another
OL,10,Findependence referendum.
OL,12,F"But pro-UK voters can prevent that
OL,13,Fnightmare scenario by backing the
OL,14,FScottish Conservatives on their peach
OL,15,Fballot on Thursday."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@TO]
